---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { ROADMAP_FORM_ACTION, CONTACT } from "../config";
---

<Base
  title="Free: The 30-Day AI & Quantum Readiness Roadmap"
  description="A free, conservative 30-day roadmap for government contractors facing AI-use and quantum-readiness questions: what's binding, what's guidance, and the order to address it."
  docId="QSOP-WEB-004"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Free Download · Lead Resource</p>
      <h1>The 30-Day AI &amp; Quantum Readiness Roadmap</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        What agencies are actually asking in 2026, what's binding versus guidance, and a
        realistic 30-day order of operations — awareness and disclosure first, inventory
        second, decisions third. No fluff, no fear-selling.
      </p>

      {ROADMAP_FORM_ACTION ? (
        <form class="inline-form" method="post" action={ROADMAP_FORM_ACTION}>
          <label for="email" class="eyebrow" style="flex-basis:100%; margin-bottom:0;">Work email</label>
          <input id="email" type="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@company.com" autocomplete="email" />
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send me the roadmap</button>
        </form>
      ) : (
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href={`mailto:${CONTACT}?subject=Send%20me%20the%2030-day%20roadmap`}>
            Email me the roadmap
          </a>
        </div>
      )}

      <p class="note" style="margin-top:1.6rem; max-width:46rem;">
        You'll also receive the Sentinel briefing — occasional, signal-only updates when
        AI or PQC requirements actually change. Unsubscribe anytime. See the
        <a href="/privacy-policy">privacy policy</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">What's Covered</p>
      <h2>Days 1–30, in three phases.</h2>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Days 1–10</p>
          <h3>Awareness &amp; disclosure</h3>
          <p>Establish your official answers to "Do you use AI?" and "Are you quantum-aware?" before anyone asks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Days 11–20</p>
          <h3>Inventory &amp; alignment</h3>
          <p>Know where AI is used and where cryptography lives, so every future answer stays consistent.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="eyebrow">Days 21–30</p>
          <h3>Decide what's next</h3>
          <p>Judge whether static readiness is enough for your pipeline — or whether maintained evidence is worth it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
